# ARENA-GAME

**ARENA-GAME** is a portfolio project showcasing a fast-paced arena survival game powered by a custom C++ game engine. Fight off waves of enemies, upgrade your hero, and master a dynamic skill tree â€” all built from the ground up to demonstrate modern engine architecture and gameplay systems.

